<tr><td nowrap width="20%" valign=baseline align=right><b>Notes: </b></td><td colspan=4 align=left valign=baseline>This art was for a game that was never produced, as far as we know. We also don't know if it was ever under consideration by Bally. The Bally name does not appear on this art.<br><br>We have no date for this art, but it includes four score display windows and the two smaller credit and <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Match">match</a> windows on the right side, typical of Bally <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Backglass">backglasses</a> from 1976 to 1986.<P></td></tr>
